Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Free-Standing Commercial Building in CBD Location

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Metres from Future Light Rail Station

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive agent is pleased to present 27 Fennell St, Parramatta. The property is a two-storey freehold commercial building situated on a prominent corner block. The property boasts two street frontages with 7 secure car spaces accessible from Villers Street. Featuring open floor plans, sun drenched and newly renovated office area, the property is ready for investors or owner occupiers to occupy. Offering an array of shops, cafes, amenities, Parramatta is home to an expansive Westfield Parramatta. With exceptional connectivity, Parramatta has a major train station, serviced by buses, both to the city and other suburbs & plans for a future light rail.   


27 Fennell Street Parramatta benefits from the following key attributes:

•	Prominent corner location with huge exposure
•	Set to benefit from the upcoming Parramatta Light Rail project
•	Only metres from future Fennell Street Light Rail Station 
•	Recently renovated and ready to occupy 
•	Prime location close to array of restaurants, amenities, Parramatta Station & Westfield Parramatta
•	NLA 249sqm* with 7 secure car spaces

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

* Roller shutter access
* Bathrooms amenities with showers
* Electricity and internet wired
* Driveway parking
* Close to Parramatta CBD
* Concrete foundations
